   c) Calculate $\displaystyle\lim_{x \to 2} f(x)$ algebraically and compare with the table.</p>
<blockquote>
<p><strong>Solution:</strong></p>
<p><strong>a)</strong> The denominator vanishes at $x^2 - 4 = 0 \Rightarrow x = \pm 2$.<br />
$\text{Dom}(f) = \mathbb{R} \setminus {-2, 2}$</p>
<p><strong>b)</strong> Table for $x \to 2$:</p>
<table>
<thead>
<tr>
<th>$x$</th>
<th>$1{,}9$</th>
<th>$1{,}99$</th>
<th>$2{,}01$</th>
<th>$2{,}1$</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td>$f(x)$</td>
<td>$1{,}4262$</td>
<td>$1{,}4925$</td>
<td>$1{,}5075$</td>
<td>$1{,}5732$</td>
</tr>
